projecttitle: Autonomous integrated irrigation systems based on wind turbines, small hydro and photovoltaic installations
project_descrip: Short: AUTONOMOUS INTEGRATED IRRIGATION SYSTEMS BASED ON WIND TURBINES, SMALL HYDRO AND PHOTOVOLTAIC INSTALLATIONS Long: Creating systems for drip or sprinkler irrigation systems integrated with energy conversion systems (wind, hydro and solar photovoltaic) and computerized intelligent and interactive control by managing simultaneously irrigation, fertilization and phytosanitary treatments application processes
shortdescription: AUTONOMOUS INTEGRATED IRRIGATION SYSTEMS BASED ON WIND TURBINES, SMALL HYDRO AND PHOTOVOLTAIC INSTALLATIONS
longdescription: Creating systems for drip or sprinkler irrigation systems integrated with energy conversion systems (wind, hydro and solar photovoltaic) and computerized intelligent and interactive control by managing simultaneously irrigation, fertilization and phytosanitary treatments application processes
